WEBVTT

00:00:04.175 --> 00:00:05.343
[A18 GASPS]

00:00:07.582 --> 00:00:09.553
[CELL]
You forget... I know you.

00:00:09.586 --> 00:00:12.291
You can't help but be curious
to see what I'll become;

00:00:12.324 --> 00:00:13.795
it's in your blood.

00:00:13.828 --> 00:00:16.701
Your race lives for
the thrill of battle.

00:00:16.734 --> 00:00:19.607
The stronger your opponent
the more you welcome it.

00:00:19.640 --> 00:00:22.813
Anything that gives you
a chance to test your mettle.

00:00:22.846 --> 00:00:24.315
It's true, isn't it.

00:00:24.348 --> 00:00:25.585
You know I'm right.

00:00:25.618 --> 00:00:27.723
You want to see
my full power.

00:00:27.756 --> 00:00:30.494
Your pride won't let
you have it any other way.

00:00:30.528 --> 00:00:32.566
And not just your pride...

00:00:32.599 --> 00:00:34.603
You are the Prince
of the Saiyans.

00:00:34.636 --> 00:00:36.707
The pride of your
entire warrior race

00:00:36.740 --> 00:00:38.811
rests on your shoulders.

00:01:08.771 --> 00:01:13.781
♪ opening song ♪

00:02:14.335 --> 00:02:16.473
[CELL]
Unless you face me
in my perfect form,

00:02:16.507 --> 00:02:18.911
you'll never really know if
you're the most powerful warrior

00:02:18.944 --> 00:02:21.349
in the universe, will you?

00:02:24.723 --> 00:02:26.927
[VEGETA LAUGHS]

00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:27.895
You do know me well.

00:02:27.929 --> 00:02:30.568
I'd be lying if
I said I wasn't intrigued.

00:02:30.601 --> 00:02:31.604
Say what...?!

00:02:31.637 --> 00:02:32.839
Alright then...

00:02:32.872 --> 00:02:35.845
I'll allow myself to be
goaded into your trap.

00:02:35.878 --> 00:02:38.785
Go on, obtain this
so-called "perfect form."

00:02:38.818 --> 00:02:41.857
No, Dad...! Stop him!
If you let him go now--

00:02:41.890 --> 00:02:42.992
[VEGETA]
Silence Trunks!

00:02:43.026 --> 00:02:45.865
I would take no pride in
defeating this pathetic worm

00:02:45.898 --> 00:02:46.967
in his current state.

00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:48.771
[TRUNKS]
Forget your
pride for once!

00:02:48.804 --> 00:02:50.407
There's too
much at stake!

00:02:50.440 --> 00:02:53.380
I said... Silence!

00:02:53.413 --> 00:02:54.783
Go... Now.

00:02:58.490 --> 00:03:00.562
I'll be right
here waiting, Cell.

00:03:00.595 --> 00:03:01.963
[CELL LAUGHS]

00:03:02.899 --> 00:03:03.901
Ahh...

00:03:06.907 --> 00:03:09.713
My father might condone
this... but I will not!

00:03:09.746 --> 00:03:11.616
[CELL GROWLS]

00:03:13.954 --> 00:03:15.525
Sorry, Bulma...

00:03:15.558 --> 00:03:19.566
I know how hard you
worked on this. But...

00:03:21.737 --> 00:03:22.973
[A18 GASPS]

00:03:23.006 --> 00:03:25.611
[HISSING]

00:03:26.547 --> 00:03:28.518
You have to get out of here.

00:03:28.551 --> 00:03:31.422
This'll all be for nothing
if you let Cell find you.

00:03:31.455 --> 00:03:32.491
Now go!

00:03:33.828 --> 00:03:35.932
[A18]
I don't understand.
You had me.

00:03:35.965 --> 00:03:36.734
You could have shut me down

00:03:36.767 --> 00:03:38.938
before I even realized
you were here.

00:03:38.971 --> 00:03:40.775
Why would you
just let me go?

00:03:40.808 --> 00:03:43.680
Well... Well I...

00:03:44.749 --> 00:03:46.921
Move it, boy!

00:03:46.954 --> 00:03:49.492
I don't have the patience
to deal with you right now.

00:03:49.526 --> 00:03:51.496
I have an android to find!

00:03:51.530 --> 00:03:54.603
You can forget about reaching
your perfect form, Cell.

00:03:54.636 --> 00:03:55.137
What?!

00:03:55.170 --> 00:03:55.872
If you want Eighteen,

00:03:55.905 --> 00:03:57.976
you'll have to
get past me first.

00:03:58.009 --> 00:04:01.416
Why you... Fine!
If that's the way you want it!

00:04:01.449 --> 00:04:02.686
[CELL YELLS]

00:04:02.719 --> 00:04:05.457
[FIGHTING SOUNDS]

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:11.736
[CELL GRUNTS]

00:04:13.641 --> 00:04:15.477
[SPLASH]

00:04:15.511 --> 00:04:17.481
[CELL GRUNTS]

00:04:17.515 --> 00:04:19.987
[VEGETA] Trunks...!
Don't interfere!

00:04:20.020 --> 00:04:21.957
Yeah, control your brat!

00:04:21.990 --> 00:04:25.832
Get up here and do
something before I--

00:04:25.865 --> 00:04:26.867
[CELL GASPS]

00:04:32.512 --> 00:04:34.816
[CELL THINKING]
Android Eighteen...

00:04:34.849 --> 00:04:36.853
I've found her!

00:04:39.091 --> 00:04:39.993
Oh, no!

00:04:41.997 --> 00:04:42.966
[CELL THINKING]
I knew it...!

00:04:42.999 --> 00:04:44.770
I knew she was close!

00:04:44.803 --> 00:04:48.945
She's been right here under
my nose this whole time!

00:04:48.978 --> 00:04:50.080
It's really happening!

00:04:50.114 --> 00:04:54.088
I will finally realize
the full potential of my design!

00:04:54.121 --> 00:04:57.963
The ultimate strength!
Speed! Agility! Intellect...!

00:04:57.996 --> 00:05:00.734
At last,
I will know perfection!

00:05:01.970 --> 00:05:03.039
[TRUNKS]
What are they doing?!

00:05:03.072 --> 00:05:06.478
They aren't even paying
attention to us over here!

00:05:10.020 --> 00:05:12.592
I thought...
you wanted to destroy us.

00:05:12.625 --> 00:05:14.563
So why smash the controller?

00:05:14.596 --> 00:05:16.766
Well... because uh...

00:05:18.069 --> 00:05:20.073
[KRILLIN THINKING]
I can't even get two words out

00:05:20.106 --> 00:05:22.979
with her looking
at me like that.

00:05:23.012 --> 00:05:25.117
Look, the reason's not
important right now!

00:05:25.150 --> 00:05:25.952
All that matters
is getting you

00:05:25.985 --> 00:05:27.989
as far away from
Cell as possible!

00:05:28.022 --> 00:05:30.795
So go... If you stay here
and Cell absorbs you,

00:05:30.828 --> 00:05:33.033
that means game over
for the whole world!

00:05:33.066 --> 00:05:35.037
[A18 GASPS]

00:05:35.070 --> 00:05:36.139
[TRUNKS] Hey!

00:05:36.172 --> 00:05:38.544
You've been spotted!
Run for it!

00:05:38.577 --> 00:05:39.011
What?!

00:05:39.044 --> 00:05:40.079
Huh...?

00:05:42.619 --> 00:05:43.620
[A18 GASPS]

00:05:47.862 --> 00:05:50.100
Don't even think about it!

00:05:50.133 --> 00:05:51.703
[TRUNKS YELLS]

00:05:54.943 --> 00:05:56.780
Excellent...

00:05:56.813 --> 00:05:59.819
It's looking like I won't
have to wait very long at all.

00:06:07.234 --> 00:06:08.537
[TRUNKS YELLS]

00:06:09.906 --> 00:06:14.549
[MULTIPLE EXPLOSIONS]

00:06:18.022 --> 00:06:20.159
[FIGHTING SOUNDS]

00:06:28.109 --> 00:06:29.111
All right...!

00:06:41.035 --> 00:06:43.173
His energy's disappeared!

00:06:43.206 --> 00:06:44.241
Watch out!

00:06:44.275 --> 00:06:46.846
Cell's masking his power
and moving underground!

00:06:50.120 --> 00:06:52.591
Hey come on...
We need to go!

00:06:53.861 --> 00:06:55.030
[A18]
Yeah. Right...

00:06:55.063 --> 00:06:57.034
Come on, Sixteen.

00:06:57.067 --> 00:06:59.973
Sixteen, get up!

00:07:00.006 --> 00:07:03.213
Leave me... Go.
Save yourself.

00:07:03.246 --> 00:07:06.954
I can do nothing for
you but slow you down.

00:07:06.987 --> 00:07:08.757
Go on, run!

00:07:16.172 --> 00:07:17.709
[EXPLOSION]

00:07:17.742 --> 00:07:19.746
[A18 AND KRILLIN YELL]

00:07:19.779 --> 00:07:22.117
[CELL] Eighteen...

00:07:23.987 --> 00:07:26.860
[CELL LAUGHS]

00:07:28.897 --> 00:07:30.033
[TRUNKS YELLS]

00:07:31.903 --> 00:07:33.808
This is my fight
to win, Trunks!

00:07:33.841 --> 00:07:36.111
You will not
rob me of my glory!

00:07:41.288 --> 00:07:42.223
Huh...?

00:07:44.161 --> 00:07:45.163
[VEGETA YELLS]

00:07:45.196 --> 00:07:46.198
Ahh...!

00:07:47.702 --> 00:07:48.704
Hmph...

00:07:52.010 --> 00:07:54.115
[CELL LAUGHS]

00:07:54.148 --> 00:07:57.153
Nice to see
you again, Eighteen.

00:08:00.193 --> 00:08:01.195
Huh...?

00:08:02.130 --> 00:08:03.132
[BUZZING]

00:08:05.069 --> 00:08:06.940
Don't push your luck, Sixteen.

00:08:06.973 --> 00:08:09.311
You look like you're on the
verge of shutdown as it is.

00:08:09.344 --> 00:08:11.182
[BUZZING]

00:08:11.215 --> 00:08:15.223
Besides, Vegeta has decided to
help me obtain my perfect form.

00:08:15.256 --> 00:08:17.194
You'd have to contend
with him as well.

00:08:17.227 --> 00:08:19.800
Vegeta...
That traitor...!

00:08:19.833 --> 00:08:22.271
So... let's get
on with the feast.

00:08:22.304 --> 00:08:26.245
I've been looking forward
to this meal for a long time.

00:08:28.082 --> 00:08:30.053
Ahh...
Vegeta...!

00:08:30.086 --> 00:08:32.725
[BULMA]
What? What about Vegeta?

00:08:32.758 --> 00:08:34.295
Is something wrong?

00:08:34.328 --> 00:08:35.765
Hey!

00:08:35.798 --> 00:08:37.802
I'm talking to
you back here!

00:08:37.835 --> 00:08:41.075
What's going on?
Spit it out!

00:08:41.108 --> 00:08:43.046
[PICCOLO THINKING]
What's taking so long, Goku?

00:08:43.079 --> 00:08:45.249
Get out here and
stop this madness!

00:08:48.089 --> 00:08:50.227
What are you doing, Cell?
Get on with it...!

00:08:50.260 --> 00:08:53.299
You aren't going to accomplish
anything by stalling!

00:08:53.332 --> 00:08:55.036
[CELL LAUGHS]

00:08:58.877 --> 00:09:00.180
[KRILLIN]
Why you...!

00:09:00.213 --> 00:09:02.985
[KRILLIN YELLS]

00:09:04.254 --> 00:09:05.825
Little pest...

00:09:05.858 --> 00:09:06.860
[THUD]

00:09:08.129 --> 00:09:10.233
[A16 YELLS]

00:09:10.266 --> 00:09:11.970
Good effort, Sixteen.

00:09:12.003 --> 00:09:12.972
It's more than I'd expect from

00:09:13.005 --> 00:09:15.778
a broken down
mechanical puppet.

00:09:15.811 --> 00:09:17.314
But I do think
I've seen enough.

00:09:17.347 --> 00:09:18.984
[CELL LAUGHS]

00:09:19.017 --> 00:09:21.155
[A16 YELLS]

00:09:21.188 --> 00:09:22.324
Monster...!

00:09:22.357 --> 00:09:25.798
[A18 YELLS]

00:09:38.322 --> 00:09:40.293
[EXPLOSION]

00:09:40.326 --> 00:09:41.763
[TRUNKS YELLS]

00:09:43.332 --> 00:09:45.003
[TRUNKS]
This has
to stop, Dad!

00:09:45.036 --> 00:09:48.042
You're making
a huge mistake!

00:09:48.075 --> 00:09:50.815
What if Cell's power ends up
being too much for us?!

00:09:50.848 --> 00:09:51.984
What happens then?!

00:09:52.017 --> 00:09:53.888
Ha...
What's wrong with you?

00:09:53.921 --> 00:09:57.027
Any Saiyan would be excited
to see this "perfect form."

00:09:57.060 --> 00:10:00.333
No... I don't
need to see it!

00:10:02.070 --> 00:10:03.172
Hmm...

00:10:03.206 --> 00:10:06.279
I've already seen one future
turned into a nightmare!

00:10:06.312 --> 00:10:10.020
I'm not going to stand here
and watch it happen again!

00:10:10.053 --> 00:10:12.291
Even if that
means fighting you!

00:10:12.324 --> 00:10:13.259
[TRUNKS YELLS]

00:10:13.292 --> 00:10:14.963
Is that so?

00:10:14.996 --> 00:10:16.432
[VEGETA LAUGHS]

00:10:16.465 --> 00:10:18.069
Who are you trying to fool?!

00:10:18.102 --> 00:10:21.275
You're too soft-hearted
to attack your own father.

00:10:21.308 --> 00:10:22.812
I call your bluff.

00:10:22.845 --> 00:10:24.849
Take your best shot!

00:10:26.385 --> 00:10:27.822
Ahh...!

00:10:27.855 --> 00:10:29.257
[TRUNKS YELLS]

00:10:37.140 --> 00:10:39.344
[A18 YELLS]

00:10:43.419 --> 00:10:48.062
[A18 YELLS]

00:10:48.429 --> 00:10:50.834
[CELL LAUGHS]

00:11:03.927 --> 00:11:05.497
[KRILLIN GRUNTS]

00:11:05.531 --> 00:11:07.400
[KRILLIN GASPS]

00:11:09.371 --> 00:11:11.241
Oh man, he's got her!

00:11:12.979 --> 00:11:15.016
No... Run... Eighteen!

00:11:15.049 --> 00:11:17.354
[CELL LAUGHS]

00:11:17.387 --> 00:11:18.957
[A18 GASPS]

00:11:23.466 --> 00:11:27.374
[CELL LAUGHS]

00:11:27.407 --> 00:11:29.111
I can't watch!

00:11:29.144 --> 00:11:32.885
[CELL LAUGHS]

00:11:47.147 --> 00:11:48.517
[CELL LAUGHS]

00:11:48.550 --> 00:11:50.887
[TRUNKS YELLS]

00:11:52.792 --> 00:11:53.727
Go! Now...!

00:11:53.761 --> 00:11:56.198
Get as far away from
here as you can! Hurry!

00:11:58.002 --> 00:11:59.038
You little...!

00:11:59.071 --> 00:12:04.080
[FIGHTING SOUNDS]

00:12:14.234 --> 00:12:17.909
Leave me here...
Run, Eighteen!

00:12:17.942 --> 00:12:19.812
I won't go without you!

00:12:21.583 --> 00:12:23.219
[KRILLIN LAUGHS]

00:12:23.252 --> 00:12:25.256
You're... still here?

00:12:28.563 --> 00:12:30.868
So... he actually did it.

00:12:30.901 --> 00:12:33.974
Perhaps he's not
as soft as I thought.

00:12:39.251 --> 00:12:42.558
That disrespectful little brat!

00:12:44.962 --> 00:12:49.939
[FOOTSTEPS]

00:13:03.934 --> 00:13:07.808
[GOHAN BREATHES HEAVILY]

00:13:08.309 --> 00:13:10.046
[GOHAN GROWLS]

00:13:12.016 --> 00:13:13.018
Huh...?

00:13:14.321 --> 00:13:16.860
I passed out
again, didn't I?

00:13:16.893 --> 00:13:17.928
I'm sorry, Dad.

00:13:17.962 --> 00:13:19.364
I know I'm holding you back
from your own training.

00:13:19.397 --> 00:13:21.402
I'll try harder
next time, promise!

00:13:21.435 --> 00:13:24.843
Hey... Don't be
so hard on yourself.

00:13:24.876 --> 00:13:26.112
Going Super Saiyan
ain't easy.

00:13:26.145 --> 00:13:27.280
You'll get there.

00:13:28.382 --> 00:13:29.586
'Kay!

00:13:29.619 --> 00:13:34.829
[FIGHTING SOUNDS]

00:13:36.966 --> 00:13:39.037
[CELL GROWLS]

00:13:43.212 --> 00:13:45.917
Heh... Oh no you don't.

00:13:54.167 --> 00:13:57.007
[CELL]
You really think you
can get away from me?!

00:13:57.040 --> 00:13:57.909
[CELL LAUGHS]

00:13:57.942 --> 00:13:59.211
[A18 GASPS]

00:13:59.244 --> 00:14:03.118
There's no escape
this time... Eighteen.

00:14:05.223 --> 00:14:06.224
Ah...!

00:14:08.062 --> 00:14:10.099
That punk! Ahh...!

00:14:12.103 --> 00:14:13.973
Solar Flare!

00:14:23.693 --> 00:14:25.463
[A18]
I can't see!

00:14:25.496 --> 00:14:28.670
[TRUNKS GRUNTS]

00:14:28.703 --> 00:14:33.011
Now... I'm gonna take my time
and savor you properly.

00:14:41.361 --> 00:14:43.365
[KRILLIN SCREAMS]

00:14:46.973 --> 00:14:50.280
[CELL LAUGHS]

00:14:50.313 --> 00:14:52.952
Why you freak!

00:14:52.985 --> 00:14:56.258
[A18 SCREAMS]

00:14:56.291 --> 00:14:58.396
[CELL GROWLS]

00:14:58.429 --> 00:15:00.433
[A18 SCREAMS]

00:15:00.466 --> 00:15:06.078
[CELL SCREAMS]

00:15:06.111 --> 00:15:08.015
Let her go!

00:15:08.048 --> 00:15:11.957
[FIGHTING SOUNDS]

00:15:11.990 --> 00:15:13.125
Eight-teen!

00:15:14.027 --> 00:15:15.396
[A18 SCREAMS]

00:15:17.300 --> 00:15:20.406
[A18 SCREAMS]

00:15:22.043 --> 00:15:25.149
[TRUNKS GRUNTS]

00:15:43.753 --> 00:15:48.428
[RUMBLING]

00:15:49.732 --> 00:15:52.404
So, he really is transforming...

00:15:52.437 --> 00:15:54.241
Now we'll see if
this perfect form

00:15:54.274 --> 00:15:56.278
is all he made it out to be.

00:16:11.174 --> 00:16:13.279
[VEGETA THINKING]
Heh... He's certainly
taking his time.

00:16:13.312 --> 00:16:15.450
This had better
be worth the wait.

00:16:15.483 --> 00:16:18.488
There's no way
I'm letting this happen!

00:16:22.363 --> 00:16:26.438
[ELECTRICAL ARCING]

00:16:30.313 --> 00:16:34.054
[ELECTRICAL BUZZING]

00:16:34.087 --> 00:16:39.097
[ELECTRICAL ARCING]

00:16:58.202 --> 00:17:00.206
Something bad just
happened, didn't it?

00:17:00.239 --> 00:17:03.714
All of a sudden, it feels like
the whole tower is vibrating.

00:17:03.747 --> 00:17:05.216
Yeah, it's Cell.

00:17:05.249 --> 00:17:07.420
His energy level
just exploded.

00:17:07.453 --> 00:17:12.463
[LIGHTNING STRIKES]

00:17:27.594 --> 00:17:29.565
[LIGHTNING STRIKES]

00:17:29.598 --> 00:17:34.608
[ELECTRICAL BUZZING]

00:17:43.492 --> 00:17:45.263
[KRILLIN THINKING]
This is all my fault.

00:17:45.296 --> 00:17:46.766
Why didn't I shut down
Android Eighteen

00:17:46.799 --> 00:17:48.402
when I had the chance?!

00:17:59.759 --> 00:18:01.529
[ELECTRICAL BUZZING]

00:18:12.718 --> 00:18:17.360
Enough...! I refuse to let
you destroy another future!

00:18:17.393 --> 00:18:19.397
[TRUNKS YELLS]

00:18:21.401 --> 00:18:22.638
[TRUNKS YELLS]

00:18:24.508 --> 00:18:26.813
[TRUNKS GRUNTS]

00:18:26.846 --> 00:18:28.349
[CELL SCREAMS]

00:18:28.382 --> 00:18:29.518
[TRUNKS SCREAMS]

00:18:50.727 --> 00:18:52.464
[DENDE BREATHES HEAVILY]

00:18:52.497 --> 00:18:53.666
[DENDE]
Grand Elder!

00:18:54.267 --> 00:18:58.777
Ah, Dende... so you
sense it too, do you?

00:18:58.810 --> 00:19:01.916
Uh-huh... Whatever it is,
it feels like pure evil.

00:19:01.949 --> 00:19:04.421
Our friends back on Earth
are in terrible danger,

00:19:04.454 --> 00:19:05.591
aren't they, Elder?

00:19:05.624 --> 00:19:07.293
[MOORI] I fear
you're correct.

00:19:07.326 --> 00:19:09.899
But even worse, I fear
an evil of this magnitude

00:19:09.932 --> 00:19:11.836
could threaten
not just the Earth,

00:19:11.869 --> 00:19:14.508
but the entire
universe as well...

00:19:36.719 --> 00:19:37.454
[LIGHTNING STRIKES]

00:19:37.487 --> 00:19:40.593
[EXPLOSION]

00:20:00.800 --> 00:20:03.506
Looks like you're
finally finished.

00:20:22.945 --> 00:20:24.882
Cell has reached
his perfect form.

00:20:24.915 --> 00:20:25.950
[BULMA GASPS]

00:20:27.921 --> 00:20:29.926
But... how...?
I thought that Krillin...

00:20:29.959 --> 00:20:31.963
Didn't he use
the controller I made?

00:20:31.996 --> 00:20:34.702
What, did it not work?

00:20:34.735 --> 00:20:35.637
We'll never know...

00:20:35.670 --> 00:20:37.942
At the last second,
Krillin smashed it.

00:20:37.975 --> 00:20:39.846
[BULMA GASPS]

00:20:39.879 --> 00:20:41.883
What would possess
him to do that?!

00:20:41.916 --> 00:20:42.718
[BABY TRUNKS CRIES]

00:20:42.751 --> 00:20:45.857
Come on, Vegeta.
Don't you fail us.

00:21:21.996 --> 00:21:24.735
[NARRATOR]
Cell's dream of reaching
his perfect form

00:21:24.768 --> 00:21:26.940
has finally come true.

00:21:26.973 --> 00:21:28.543
But for the rest of the world,

00:21:28.576 --> 00:21:30.981
the nightmare is
just beginning...

00:21:31.014 --> 00:21:34.453
next Dragon Ball Z Kai!

00:22:38.750 --> 00:22:41.623
[TRUNKS]
Hey, this is Trunks.
We're in trouble.

00:22:41.656 --> 00:22:42.925
Cell's perfect form
is even mor--

00:22:42.958 --> 00:22:45.029
[VEGETA]
Ah, Trunks! How dare
you attack me?!

00:22:45.062 --> 00:22:46.131
[TRUNKS]
I'm sorry!

00:22:46.164 --> 00:22:47.601
I was only trying to stop
Cell from transforming!

00:22:47.634 --> 00:22:51.008
[VEGETA]
And what would that have proved,
defeating a worthless opponent?!

00:22:51.041 --> 00:22:52.678
I want a challenge!

00:22:52.711 --> 00:22:58.857
[GOKU] Next time,
on Dragon Ball Z Kai...

00:22:58.890 --> 00:23:01.562
[VEGETA]
It's only when were pushed
to our absolute limits

00:23:01.595 --> 00:23:04.033
that we Saiyans
can truly shine!

